left out-- Matika, you, too,

01:25:31.010 --> 01:25:34.640
come teach here-- they
need to be on our faculty.

01:25:34.640 --> 01:25:36.120
And that's not all.

01:25:36.120 --> 01:25:38.540
Harvard needs to recognize
the living reality

01:25:38.540 --> 01:25:41.500
of Native American lives,
Native American languages,

01:25:41.500 --> 01:25:44.010
Native American peoples.

01:25:44.010 --> 01:25:47.220
So today, native peoples did
native politics at Harvard.

01:25:47.220 --> 01:25:50.250
Native peoples performed
native politics.

01:25:50.250 --> 01:25:52.460
And thank you to my native
sisters and brothers

01:25:52.460 --> 01:25:53.850
for having done it.

01:25:53.850 --> 01:25:54.917
It was a beautiful.

01:25:54.917 --> 01:25:56.288
Thank you.

